               <p>He was a 2d time indicted for <rs id="t17340424-20-off92" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17340424-20-off92" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17340424-20-off92" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               forging and counterfeiting, and causing to be forg'd and counterfeited, a Receipt for 17 l. 8 s. in these Words, July 20. 1732. Receiv'd of 
                     <persName id="t17340424-20-person161">
                        Thomas 
                        Page 
                     <interp inst="t17340424-20-person161" type="surname" value="Page"></interp>
